<body>
    <h1>3- PB Influencer meets bill clearance (mason/contractor/dealer)- Op=
s process</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 id=3D"id-3-PBInfluencermeetsbillclearance(mason/contractor/deal=
er)-Opsprocess-PurposeandScope"><strong>Purpose and Scope</strong></h2>
<p>Timely calculation, verification and reimbursement of distributor bills =
for regular influencer meets organized at respective distributor locations =
for sales and promotion.</p>
<p><strong>Handover timeline: PB -&gt;BizOps: </strong><time datetime=3D"20=
25-09-08" class=3D"date-past">08 Sep 2025</time> <em>(to be aligned)</em></=
p>
<h2 id=3D"id-3-PBInfluencermeetsbillclearance(mason/contractor/dealer)-Opsp=
rocess-Stakeholders"><strong>Stakeholders</strong></h2>
<p>Influencer data updation in forms- Sales</p>
<p>Documents verification- BizOps</p>
<p>Bills processing- Finance</p>
<p>Data management platform - Excel</p>
<h2 id=3D"id-3-PBInfluencermeetsbillclearance(mason/contractor/dealer)-Opsp=
rocess-Steps"><strong>Steps</strong></h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>A google-form to be filled in by Sales team for each influencer meet, wh=
ich includes details of distrbutors, dealers, meet type, and a pdf document=
 containing bills, meet photos etc.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>For regional Sales SPOC, refer <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https:=
//jsw-my.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/personal/ajay_swami1_jsw_in/_layouts/15/Doc.a=
spx?sourcedoc=3D%7B8492BC56-6CBB-425C-B95B-3B0D49B65434%7D&amp;file=3DPB-%2=
0Sales%20Team%20Head%20count.xlsx&amp;action=3Ddefault&amp;mobileredirect=
=3Dtrue" rel=3D"nofollow">PB- Sales Team Head count.xlsx</a><a class=3D"ext=
ernal-link" href=3D"https://jsw-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ajay_swami1_jsw_=
in/_layouts/15/AccessDenied.aspx?Source=3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fjsw%2Dmy%2Esharepoi=
nt%2Ecom%2F%3Ax%3A%2Fr%2Fpersonal%2Fajay%5Fswami1%5Fjsw%5Fin%2F%5Flayouts%2=
F15%2FDoc%2Easpx%3FCT%3D1756731132342%26OR%3DOWA%2DNT%2DMail%26CID%3Def81b9=
fb%2D5584%2Dc55c%2D7357%2D27ecd46d348d%26sourcedoc%3D%257B8492BC56%2D6CBB%2=
D425C%2DB95B%2D3B0D49B65434%257D%26file%3DPB%2D%2BSales%2BTeam%2BHead%2Bcou=
nt%2Exlsx%26action%3Ddefault%26mobileredirect%3Dtrue&amp;correlation=3D2a78=
c1a1%2D0022%2D5000%2Dc538%2D0b66c6d29507&amp;Type=3Ditem&amp;name=3D573ba9c=
5%2Db998%2D42e9%2D89ab%2D3e80366ea0ef&amp;listItemId=3D407&amp;listItemUniq=
ueId=3D8492bc56%2D6cbb%2D425c%2Db95b%2D3b0d49b65434" rel=3D"nofollow"></a>l=
ist.</p>
<ol start=3D"2">
<li>
<p>The data filled in the forms will populate in excel sheet for reference =
and action. Sheet link: PPA <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://jsw-=
my.sharepoint.com/:x:/r/personal/tanvi1_jsw_in/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourced=
oc=3D%7B74FFDF07-67D9-4EF4-A24F-0050B4F8DC25%7D&amp;file=3DPPA%20Invoices%2=
0Reimbursement-%20FY%2726%20Q2%20Budget!.xlsx&amp;fromShare=3Dtrue&amp;acti=
on=3Ddefault&amp;mobileredirect=3Dtrue" rel=3D"nofollow">Invoices Reimburse=
ment- FY'26 Q2 Budget!</a>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>BizOps to scrutinize all details of the meet from the document attached =
by Sales, basis the below checkpoints as shared by Tanvi (PB HO team):</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>The bill should be strictly within budget (unless special approval is ta=
ken and attached)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Budget /pax for dealer, Architect meets is Rs 3500 (Excl GST), mason mee=
ts is Rs 300 (Excl GST), contractor meets is Rs 1000 (Excl GST). For change=
s in budget, Tanvi to update the new price in the same sheet above in 'Budg=
et Master' tab.</p></li>
<li>
<p>No supporting invoices are attached more than once in the pdf. No repeti=
tion&nbsp;of the same supporting bill.</p></li>
<li>
<p>No double GST is being charged for any supporting bill.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Spelling of JODL (JSW One Distribution Limited) to be correct. Check GST=
 no. state.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Since gifts for mason, contractor meets are being purchased collectively=
, invoice raised is for the gift qtys being used and not collective.</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>The supporting invoices amount should match the JODL invoice amount. <em=
>(Finance to check)</em></p></li>
<li>
<p>The consolidated PDF file should have cover letter, JODL invoice, suppor=
ting docs, attendance list, meeting brief, photos</p></li>
<li>
<p>Images attached in the Pdf are clear.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Duplicate bills (if any) to be put on hold.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Bill to be put on hold if food claim is being made for more than number =
of masons who have attended the meet&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>All attendees details need to be properly captured by Sales.</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>Post verification of all documents, BizOps to confirm if all bills are o=
k to be forwarded to Finance for further scrutiny and processing.</p></li>
<li>
<p>In case of any discrepancy, BizOps to connect with the respective Sales =
SPOC for correction/clarification related to the bills attached.</p></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>TAT:</strong></p>
<p>Current frequency for the activity- every quarter</p>
<p>Processing timeline for bills reimbursement- 3 weeks <em>(to be aligned)=
</em></p>
<p>Current volume of bills (approx): 100-120/month || 300-360/quarter</p>
<h2 id=3D"id-3-PBInfluencermeetsbillclearance(mason/contractor/dealer)-Opsp=
rocess-Escalationmatrix"><strong>Escalation matrix </strong></h2>
<p>In case of discrepancy in documents</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
