<p><strong>Open questions:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>How to catch duplicacy of bills if uploaded by Sales on different dates?=
 - avoiding double payouts.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Frequency to be decided monthly or quarterly- if monthly, during month-e=
nd or daily? Processing timeline/TAT to be decided basis frequency of activ=
ity.</p></li>
</ol>
